<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ج ش م:</span> <span class="c2">(جَشِمَ)</span> الْأَمْرَ مِنْ بَابِ فَهِمَ وَ <span class="c2">(تَجَشَّمَهُ)</span> أَيْ تَكَلَّفَهُ عَلَى مَشَقَّةٍ وَ <span class="c2">(جَشَّمَهُ)</span> الْأَمْرُ <span class="c2">(تَجْشِيمًا)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(أَجْشَمَهُ)</span> أَيْ كَلَّفَهُ إِيَّاهُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>